      "span_text": "As described above, OVOCs had the largest contribution to the total measured VOCs; thus, the impact of cloud/fog on OVOCs formed the main discussion. compared the mixing ratios of VOCs measured under 7 different kinds of different weather conditions, such as clear sky, fog, drizzle and so on and found that OVOCs showed strong dependence on weather conditions."
